Description:
ONE VILLAGE - The place to call home.
INVEST or BUILD in this great location and be part of the new community.
Live in this new stylish and vibrant neighborhood and enjoy the conveniences of great facilities in the surrounding area near and in One Village. Underpinning the location are sporting and aquatic facilities; Casey Complex and
Casey RACE.
Located next to One Village is the prestigious Mayfield Estate and nearby shopping centers, medical facilities and a local library for your convenience.
Closeby to schools include Casey Grammar, Cranbourne East Primary School, Cranbourne East Secondary School & Chilsolm TAFE.
With easy access to Melbourne city and surrounding parklands and reserves provides a relaxed country charm to complete the lifestyle you want.
Proposed future shopping Center and potential Cranbourne East Railway Station makes this property an excellent choice to invest or to live in !

Description:
**UNDER OFFER / UNDER CONTRACT**
CRANBOURNE EAST: Built to perfection by a quality boutique builder and used for a lengthy period of time as their primary display home, 28 Prendergast Avenue couldn't provide a young family with a better path to real estate ownership.
Only app. 6 years young, this gem is set within the popular Parks Edge estate and is surrounded by a long list of local amenities and facilities including amazing sporting complexes, extensive parkland and education options including Casey Grammar, St. Peters Secondary College and Chisholm TAFE!
After being greeted by a modern facade, you step inside to find a home offering a functional floorplan designed with space and practicality in mind. Featuring a vast formal lounge upon entry there's also a separate study and a tiled family/meals area complete with a gas log fireplace.
The hostess kitchen is sure to please any keen cook and offers stone bench tops, stainless steel appliances (including a 900mm oven and hot plate) plus a generous walk-in pantry with additional bench space.
Each of the 4 bedrooms are well proportioned and feature built-in robe facilities, the master retreat complete with a walk-in wardrobe and a lovely ensuite to match the family bathroom with separate toilet.
As you can appreciate with any high end display product, the property has been treated with the full complement of extras including an alarm system, ducted reverse cycle heating and refrigerated cooling, ducted vacuuming and a 5kW solar array!
Outside you will find a remote double garage with internal access as well as a private, secure rear yard with an under-roofline alfresco finished with extensive decking.
Within a short drive to freeway access and all of the amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne, this sensational opportunity is only moments away from the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Indoor Sports Centre. With additional shopping precincts in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club local amenities are always going to be close by, whilst the recently revamped Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre offers an abundance of cafes and restaurants. Don't forget the proposed Cranbourne East train station and the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!
If you want your family to have easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation then call before it's SELLING, SELLING ..... SOLD!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW - PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS!
Our floor plans are for representational purposes only and should be used as such. We accept no liability for the accuracy or details contained in our floor plans.

Description:
Put your own touch on this almost brand new family home!
This single-storey almost new home is one that will be sure to tick all the boxes! It's simply been made for the modern family!
Centrally located in the Cranbourne East residential area perfect for first home buyers or downsizers alike. With great location and walking distance from Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre, Casey fields, and Cranbourne library as well as only minutes away from Cranbourne train station, Casey Park shopping centre, and the popular schools such as Clyde Primary, Cranbourne East Primary, Casey Grammar, and Chisholm TAFE.
Light filled and spacious, right from the moment you open the front door and see the beautiful floating timber look laminate floorboards. Immediately you will find the large sunlit master with large WIR, and ensuite, down the hallway is the first large living space/ theater room then free-flowing contemporary open plan kitchen, dining, family and rumpus room fully equipped with Caesar stone bench tops, 900mm freestanding oven, 5 burner cooktop, tiled splash back and stainless steel dishwasher all tastefully styled with modern neutral tones. The family living area is carpeted for comfort and sliding door access to the yard. Un-landscaped, this rear yard is a blank canvas ready and waiting for you to put that personal touch to it.
The rear wing of the home completes the accommodation featuring another 2 bedrooms all with BIR, central family bathroom, separate toilet .
Other features include Double remote garage with internal and external access, ducted heating, colour bond fencing and laundry with side access.
Don't miss out on this one. Enquire today!

Description:
MUST BE SOLD!
Nestled in a fantastic pocket in the new & popular Parks Edge Estate, this modern four bedroom home offers generous living space as well as a convenient lifestyle. There is literally nothing to do but enjoy the abundance of fantastic facilities nearby with your family and low maintenance living at its best.
Features include:
- Large light filled Master bedroom with WIR as well as its own ensuite.
- A further three generously sized bedrooms all with built in robes.
- Two separate living areas to enjoy – a luxurious open plan living area including dining and family space PLUS a separate formal lounge/ parents retreat.
- A beautiful kitchen showcasing stone benches, stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, gas cooktop and oven plus walk in pantry and breakfast bar to complete the picture.
- Outdoor alfresco area – perfect to kick back with a glass of wine and entertain guests.
- EXTRAS include: Double remote garage with internal access to the home, ducted heating throughout, split system a/c, stone benches to all bathrooms, ceiling fans to all bedrooms plus loads more.
Conveniently located in Cranbourne East close to Casey Fields and Casey RACE Recreation and Aquatic Centre plus nearby you will also find bus services, easy access to schools such as Cranbourne East Primary and Secondary Schools and much, much more! The perfect choice for those looking for a home to enjoy with their family in an ideal quiet location!

Description:
Approx 26 squares - Hunt Club
Located in the heart of the HUNT CLUB, one of the most sort after estates of Cranbourne East is this beautiful family home ideal for first home buyers and investors alike.
Nestled on a picturesque tree-lined street, this immaculate property features 3 spacious bedrooms PLUS a study/ 4th bedroom, Master with ensuite and BIR's, whilst the remaining 2 bedrooms have built in robes and are of good size with the added bonus of a separate study or potential 4th bedroom.
The kitchen offers ample bench and cupboard space, dishwasher and s/s appliances. Coupled with a separate formal dining area your dinner parties and covered.
The two separate living areas provides enough room for both parents and kids, with a spacious front lounge and an informal family area at the rear with access to the alfresco. Outside you'll find lush established gardens back and front.
The large alfresco area is ideal to enjoy with friends and family all year round- complete with cafe blinds you won't need to worry about the weather spoiling home events ever again!
Added extras include; ducted heating, evaporative cooling, color bond fencing, garden shed for storage and a triple garage for the motoring enthusiast.
A fantastic location within seconds walk to the Hunt Club shopping village, Wetlands, walking/bicycle paths, childcare, primary and secondary schools and public transport.
What are you waiting for? Don't miss out on this one!
Features:
- Master with full ensuite & WIR.
- 2 Large separate living areas.
- Study/ 4th Bedroom
- Large all-weather alfresco area overlooking backyard.
- Heating and cooling.
This home is ideal for investors or first home buyers. Don't miss out.

Description:
ENTERTAINERS DELIGHT!
If you are looking for a property offering outstanding value for money with literally nothing to do but unpack and relax then you have come to the right address!
Perfectly suited to growing families in a location that is second to none - literally seconds to the local bus stop providing easy transport to the recently revamped Cranbourne Centro Shopping centre and brand new Hunt Club Village Shopping centre which is situated directly opposite to the estate!
The generous sized master bedroom comes complete with walk in robes and a full ensuite!

Added features include: ducted heating and split system cooling, neutral tones throughout, paved driveway, rear roller door and completely renovated bathroom areas. All this and a whole lot more!

Masterchef quality kitchen + monster outdoor to entertain
Sitting on a generous 576 sqm is this excellent family home in the high desirable Hunt Club Estate. This home offers a unique opportunity for the growing family with great combination of flexible living space, outdoor living and to top it off a premium kitchen fit out with all the upgrades.
Features include:
- Spacious Master suite with walk in robe and ensuite.
- Three further large bedrooms all with and built in robes.
- A study for those who work from home or 5th bedroom (if converted).
- Two generous living zones to enjoy – a large formal lounge upon entry as well as a combined open plan family and dining area centred by the kitchen.
- STUNNING display quality kitchen with all the upgrades Inc. 900mm oven with 5 burner cooktop, dishwasher, 40mm Caesar stone waterfall bench top, metallic glass splashback, soft close cupboards and draws, plumbed fridge area, wine rack, utility cupboard, several pot draws, under mount sink… the list goes on!
- MASSIVE undercover outdoor entertainment area – perfect to host a special event with family and friends
- Large enough backyard for kids and pets to run around.
- Double lock up garage with rear roller door access and plenty of extra storage inside.
- EXTRAS include: Ducted Heating, Split System cooling, LED down lights, built in speakers in the family living area and the outdoor area, TV brackets for TV's, built in cabinetry in family living area and study, quality window furnishings and fittings as well as ceiling fans, electric roller shutters, a tranquil water feature in the outdoor area, large garden shed at rear, color bond fencing and lots more.
This home is located within a very short walking distance to the Cranbourne East Primary and Secondary schools, child care centres, kindergarten, numerous parks, wetlands, public transport and HUNT CLUB shopping centre. This is a perfect opportunity for a large family, first home buyers or even a savvy investor looking for a quality home in a great area. Description:
EXCEPTIONAL FAMILY LIVING!
Located in the prestigious Mayfield estate sits this impeccable example of family living!
A top tier home with an array of separate living zones, elegant outdoor entertaining area, this exquisite residence is extremely versatile and is sure to accommodate everyone's needs.
This gorgeous 4 bedroom plus study home comes complete with a large scale master bedroom equipped with walk in robes and a full en suite including dual vanities, and an over sized shower space!
The hostess kitchen is a chef's dream and is complete with quality stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, 900mm range hood, 5-burner gas cook top, caesar stone bench tops, glass splash back, ample overhead storage and bench space, not to mention a walk in pantry. All of this overlooking your separate meals zone and rear living area!
Not only is this home fitted out with top quality fixtures and fittings it also presents a grand capacity to accommodate even the largest of families, this is truly an entertainers delight with multiple living zones on offer and theater room!
Added features include: ducted heating & evaporative cooling, neutral tones throughout, manicured gardens, plantation shutters throughout, internal access to your double lock up garage plus an exposed aggregate drive way, all of this and more!
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre.
From front to back this home was completed with an exceptional eye for detail and will be the perfect residence for those that expect nothing but the best!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*

Description:
Family Haven in the Hunt Club Estate
Well-presented spacious four bedroom family home with all the essentials for fine family living and entertaining. Offering four bedrooms, two separate living areas, kitchen offers stainless steel appliances with ample bench and cupboard space. Master bedroom with en-suite and walk in robe. Other three spacious bedrooms with BIRs. Outside you will find a large undercover area with wooden decking. Double lock up garage with internal access. Other features include ducted heating, split reverse cycle air-conditioning, quality blinds, roller shutters to the master bedroom, ceiling fans, security door, dishwasher, down lights and Recycled Water plus lots more! Situated on a corner allotment of approx. 532m2 in size, there is the possibility of side access and the property has long driveway which is ideal for a multiple car parking, boat and caravan, an absolute rarity in this area. Very quiet circuit, with not a lot of traffic, let the children play with lots of room across the road.
Country living at its finest as there is no houses to look at across the road as it being the water works land. This properties location features a lovely 2 minute walk to the school and a short walk to local day care centre, public transport, hunt club village and minutes away to the heart of the Cranbourne shopping precinct. A newly developed walking/running track will keep you fit and the children will enjoy the nearby play park. Inspection of this family home is a must!

Description:
Charming ex display with 4 bed, study + living areas
This young, modern and meticulously presented home provides surprisingly a large amount of accommodation to cater for the growing family. Located in the heart of the beautiful Mayfield estate-you simply can't beat the convenient location, quality upgrades, and appliances plus family friendly layout on offer.
Comprising of:
- Spacious Master suite with separate WIR plus en-suite with oversized shower and rainwater showerhead.
- Three more generous bedrooms all with BIR's.
- TWO separate living areas to enjoy-a formal lounge/ theatre room at the front of the home with a raised floor (perfect for movie nights) PLUS an open plan living/ dining area at the rear.
- Stunning designer kitchen with plenty of upgrades such as stone benches, dishwasher, 900mm oven with 5 burner gas cooktop, breakfast bar and built-in pantry.
- A separate study-ideal if you work from home or need space for the kids to do their homework.
- The outdoor of this home offers a great place to enjoy time with friends and family – stacker doors open up to an undercover alfresco and top it off there is plenty of backyard for the kids and pets to play.
Extras in the property include: Alarm system, ducted heating/cooling, downlights throughout, mirrored sliding doors to all bedrooms, landscaped gardens, double remote garage with an internal access door and much, much more…
Mayfield Estate is well sought after master planned community in the City of Casey, featuring a children's nature garden and woodlands area, a future sports precinct and easy access to Casey Fields. You're also a short drive away from an array of amenities including Cranbourne Town Centre, Casey RACE aquatic centre and a number of schools and education centres.
With nothing to do but move in and enjoy-we know you will fall in love! Please contact us to organise your inspection before it's gone!

Description:
WHY BUILD WHEN YOU CAN MOVE IN HERE STRAIGHT AWAY?
Less than a year old, this Frenken built home is basically brand new and will appeal to buyers who like the thought of building but don't want to have to wait a year or 2 for their home to be finished. Sitting pretty on a bigger block than many estates can offer, the home is sized for a family and features a generous lounge/dining area flanked by the stunning kitchen with stone benches, stainless appliances and a large walk-in pantry as well as an additional rumpus/games room. There are 4 robed bedrooms and 2 stylish bathrooms including an ensuite in the main bedroom. Ducted heating, evaporative cooling and a split system air conditioner provide a tailored climate. The backyard is huge with a north facing position, alfresco area, large exposed aggregate patio and a garden shed for added storage as well as solar panels for your power needs. Situated in the Hunt Club right near everything from Casey Fields Sports Complex, Casey RACE, Chisholm TAFE and all of central Cranbourne's facilities, a great location only enhances its appeal.
